<text top="73" left="90" width="107" height="14" font="1">Fifty-second year</text>
<text top="73" left="730" width="98" height="14" font="1">13 August 1997</text>
<text top="109" left="153" width="295" height="14" font="1">"The Security Council will remain seized of the</text>
<text top="127" left="122" width="49" height="14" font="1">matter."</text>
<text top="163" left="122" width="327" height="14" font="1">This statement will be issued as a document of the</text>
<text top="181" left="90" width="325" height="14" font="1">Security Council under the symbol S/PRST/1997/43.</text>
<text top="109" left="512" width="316" height="14" font="1">The Security Council has thus concluded the present</text>
<text top="127" left="481" width="321" height="14" font="1">stage of its consideration of the item on the agenda.</text>
<text top="164" left="512" width="174" height="14" font="5"><i>The meeting rose at 11 a.m.</i></text>
<text top="1084" left="821" width="8" height="14" font="1">3</text>
</page>
